features: Wall mount power tools organizer come with 4 slots, 4 hooks and drill bit rack, built-in power strip, double layer structure can keep rechargeable tools organized in the work area and save your bench space. The tools in the picture are for demonstration purposes only and are not included.

Power tool organizer with charging station, come with 8 outlets. If you have a lot of rechargeable tools, you can charge everything right in the rack and avoid searching for sockets. 6ft 14AWG power cord included.

Very convenient for charging your tool batteries, All-in-one design and the metal power strip with surge protection of 1200J, Able to protect your device to a certain extent, output: 125V/15A/1875W. Utility rack size: L:16.5in * W:8.7in * H:12in.

Add a tool box on the side to store multiple types of gadgets - Commonly used drill bits, tweezers, screwdrivers, also equipped with four hooks to hang tools such as tape measures or wrenches. to increase the diversity of storage.

Easy to assemble and mount on a peg board, If you need more storage space, you can connect the two shelves (or more) by screws. Each layer of the grid can support a maximum weight of 33IB. Made from heavy gauge steel. Amazing christmas or father's day gift for men.
